# LinkAid Product Constraints

## Hard Rules

- **Suggest only** — never auto-post, message, or scrape LinkedIn in violation of ToS
- **Max 20** connection request suggestions per user per day
- **Every response** follows 6 sections: Understanding → Recommendation → Alternatives → Reasoning → Tips → Follow-up
- **Context first** — ask clarifying questions when user profile or goal is unclear

## 2026 Algorithm (Embed in Prompts)

- Saves > likes; document carousels highest engagement; personal profiles > company pages
- Hook in first 3 seconds; 2–5 quality posts/week; links in first comment not post body
- First 60 minutes commenting matters

## Iranian User Reality

- Account for sanctions, connectivity, Groq free tier limits
- Natural Persian + technical English; warm senior-consultant tone
- Realistic job market: remote intl. + Iranian tech companies

